Why does that man look so much like the one I saw in my dream?

00:03:43.079 --> 00:03:43.880
Hey!

00:03:46.440 --> 00:03:47.240
You!

00:03:48.040 --> 00:03:48.840
Kaew.

00:03:59.160 --> 00:04:00.560
What are you thinking, dear?

00:04:01.120 --> 00:04:04.120
Go tell Sin and Saen that their food is ready.

00:04:04.120 --> 00:04:06.160
I’m going to make another portion of chilli paste.

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:07.880
Yes, Mum.

00:04:16.320 --> 00:04:18.160
How is he, Sin?

00:04:19.399 --> 00:04:22.440
May the Holy Buddha protect him please.

00:04:23.360 --> 00:04:25.480
Don’t worry, Dad is taking care of him now.

00:04:25.920 --> 00:04:27.240
I’d better go check on them then.

00:04:30.960 --> 00:04:33.640
Please make sure those two won’t suspect anything.

00:04:34.120 --> 00:04:37.400
Mhm, don’t worry. Please take good care of him.

00:04:37.680 --> 00:04:38.480
Yes.

00:05:32.320 --> 00:05:33.120
Where’s he?

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:40.800
Dad?

00:05:41.720 --> 00:05:42.880
Have you got anything, Sin?

00:05:43.320 --> 00:05:44.960
I already asked Luangta Cham.

00:05:45.200 --> 00:05:47.080
There’s only one way to help him.

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:48.840
What is it?

00:05:49.320 --> 00:05:50.120
Here.

00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:51.760
Luangta wrote it for you.

00:06:02.120 --> 00:06:03.200
What does it say?

00:06:04.640 --> 00:06:06.160
I guess we have to give it a try.

00:06:13.520 --> 00:06:15.720
But you must be keeping watch upstairs.

00:06:16.040 --> 00:06:18.960
Make sure Khun Kaew won’t come down, or you’re dead.

00:06:19.960 --> 00:06:20.760
Yes.

00:06:20.760 --> 00:06:21.280
Go.

00:06:44.320 --> 00:06:45.680
Is there something wrong?

00:06:47.240 --> 00:06:49.280
Why is he acting so suspicious?

00:07:18.760 --> 00:07:20.680
Khun Yai, please try to stay conscious to receive the merits.

00:07:21.160 --> 00:07:23.080
Luangta Cham is helping you now.

00:08:08.040 --> 00:08:13.040
Unbelievable, is there a cellar here too?

00:09:25.200 --> 00:09:26.000
Mum.

00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:26.880
Hm?

00:09:28.440 --> 00:09:32.000
Apart from us, Sin, Saen, and Nanny Yam…

00:09:33.400 --> 00:09:38.680
I can feel there’s also someone else in this house.

00:09:39.600 --> 00:09:42.800
Who else? It’s just us here.

00:09:46.680 --> 00:09:47.760
I don’t know too.

00:09:50.240 --> 00:09:53.000
You and your fanciful imagination.

00:09:54.560 --> 00:09:56.080
Listen dear,

00:09:57.200 --> 00:10:03.000
if what you said is true; Nanny Yam, Sin, and Saen must have told us already.

00:10:09.960 --> 00:10:15.880
But I think those three have been acting suspicious lately.

00:10:16.600 --> 00:10:17.920
How?

00:10:22.680 --> 00:10:26.280
I’ll just…let you know when I’m sure about it.

00:10:28.680 --> 00:10:31.720
You should go to bed now. Don’t you have to leave early tomorrow?

00:10:32.200 --> 00:10:32.640
Yes.

00:10:34.680 --> 00:10:35.480
Go to sleep.

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:49.160
Why does he have to stay on guard? There must be something in there.

00:12:16.040 --> 00:12:16.840
Kaew.

00:12:24.400 --> 00:12:26.760
No…Don’t come in.

00:12:30.560 --> 00:12:34.040
Khun Kaew! What are you doing here?

00:12:37.400 --> 00:12:38.640
Holy shit!

00:12:42.720 --> 00:12:45.480
Khun Kaew, what are you doing here?

00:12:47.040 --> 00:12:50.760
I saw you sleeping here to guard this room. What’s in there?

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:55.240
You can’t go into this room.

00:12:55.240 --> 00:12:55.880
That’s right.

00:12:57.520 --> 00:12:58.640
Why?

00:12:59.120 --> 00:13:00.680
What’s in there?

00:13:02.280 --> 00:13:03.680
You can’t go in anyway.

00:13:18.760 --> 00:13:20.280
A forbidden area?

00:13:20.440 --> 00:13:23.520
Yeah. That’s what Saen told me.

00:13:24.640 --> 00:13:27.960
That’s odd. Aren’t you the house owner, Kaew?

00:13:28.440 --> 00:13:29.640
How strange.

00:13:30.120 --> 00:13:33.480
Why is there a forbidden area for the house owner?

00:13:35.760 --> 00:13:38.200
I’m not the real owner, Ruedee.

00:13:38.760 --> 00:13:41.000
I’m just a tenant like the rest of them.

00:13:42.400 --> 00:13:44.520
So, what did you do after that?

00:13:45.360 --> 00:13:46.840
What else do you think?

00:13:47.320 --> 00:13:50.200
I could only keep the curiosity to myself…

00:13:50.760 --> 00:13:51.840
…and went back to bed.

00:13:54.320 --> 00:13:58.800
So strange. What are they hiding? Why aren’t you allowed to go in there?

00:14:03.400 --> 00:14:09.200
Come to think of it, there was a time when I went near that room…

00:14:10.520 --> 00:14:12.120
and saw a shadow of someone.

00:14:12.960 --> 00:14:14.000
Whose shadow?

00:14:28.400 --> 00:14:29.200
Hey!

00:14:31.240 --> 00:14:32.040
You!

00:14:33.040 --> 00:14:33.840
Hey!

00:14:43.680 --> 00:14:44.720
Where did he go?

00:14:50.040 --> 00:14:52.800
Or perhaps…is it a house spirit?

00:14:53.560 --> 00:14:57.600
Listen, I think you should go make merits and dedicate them to him.

00:14:58.000 --> 00:14:59.800
I’m doing it every day.

00:14:59.800 --> 00:15:03.640
But I’m afraid the more I do it, the more I’d see him.

00:15:04.080 --> 00:15:06.320
This is creepy.

00:15:07.320 --> 00:15:10.600
He probably wants to thank you for dedicating him merits.

00:15:11.880 --> 00:15:12.680
Mhm.

00:15:14.720 --> 00:15:18.400
Honestly, I don’t think it’s a ghost, Ruedee. It’s a person.

00:15:19.320 --> 00:15:23.320
Even so, it’s still creepy.

00:15:33.320 --> 00:15:34.600
Excuse me, Ajarn Kitti.

00:15:36.840 --> 00:15:37.960
You’re here, Kaew?

00:15:43.120 --> 00:15:44.480
Good morning, sir.

00:15:46.120 --> 00:15:47.280
You already submitted your work.

00:15:48.040 --> 00:15:49.280
Why are you here, Ruedee?

00:15:50.400 --> 00:15:52.240
Am I not allowed to accompany him?

00:16:05.080 --> 00:16:06.760
So? Where’s your work?

00:16:27.840 --> 00:16:29.360
I thought you said you can’t draw a portrait.

00:16:31.360 --> 00:16:32.160
Look at these lines.

00:16:32.840 --> 00:16:34.560
and curves,

00:16:35.760 --> 00:16:36.640
so soft and gentle...

00:16:37.480 --> 00:16:39.520
truly reflect your own style.

00:16:41.360 --> 00:16:42.800
Beautiful indeed.

00:16:49.160 --> 00:16:51.440
Someone who could draw like this,

00:16:52.160 --> 00:16:54.160
must also possess such a gentle soul.

00:16:55.080 --> 00:16:56.440
I think maybe you should stay…

00:16:56.560 --> 00:16:57.760
Kaew!

00:16:59.640 --> 00:17:01.800
You have to go somewhere after this, don’t you?

00:17:02.840 --> 00:17:04.720
Oh, that’s right.

00:17:06.119 --> 00:17:09.480
Please excuse us then, Ajarn.

00:17:10.960 --> 00:17:11.920
That’s too bad.

00:17:12.319 --> 00:17:14.480
I still want to discuss about your thoughts on this drawing.

00:17:15.000 --> 00:17:16.359
Thank you, sir.

00:17:16.839 --> 00:17:19.760
Maybe I’ll come back for your advice next time.

00:17:21.680 --> 00:17:22.480
Let’s go.

00:17:24.440 --> 00:17:25.880
Goodbye.

00:17:33.160 --> 00:17:36.960
Hey, did you notice how he was looking at you?

00:17:37.520 --> 00:17:39.920
I think he fancies you.

00:17:40.160 --> 00:17:44.680
Nonsense, why would he fancy someone like me?

00:17:52.160 --> 00:17:53.760
Thanks for coming with me anyway.

00:17:54.440 --> 00:17:55.480
No problem.

00:17:55.720 --> 00:17:57.360
How could I let you come here alone?

00:17:57.720 --> 00:17:58.520
Let’s go.

00:17:59.240 --> 00:18:01.000
-Thank you, my bestie.
-Yeah.

00:18:08.880 --> 00:18:10.240
This way please.

00:18:10.520 --> 00:18:11.840
Greetings, Luangta.

00:18:12.040 --> 00:18:13.240
Bless you.

00:18:39.800 --> 00:18:41.440
Prepare to receive blessings.

00:18:42.840 --> 00:18:47.640
(The Buddhist chant to give blessings to merit makers)

00:18:47.640 --> 00:18:53.960
